WHAT IT IS?
Long-lasting and mosturising
Has a matte finish
Long lasting and transfer proof
Excellent coverage and high color pay off
Contains a generous helping of Vitamin E and gives you opaque pigmentation.
This products is dermatologically tested and approved and 100% safe for your skin
WHAT IT DOES?
The SUGAR Smudge Me Not Liquid Lipstick gives you opaque pigmentation with a single swipe that stays all day with zero feathering or fading.
Our favourite mattifying fix contains a generous helping of Vitamin E and comes in a full range of 20 gorgeous shades that is guaranteed to make your OOTDs stand out.

For precise application, apply it to your bottom lip first and then tend to your upper lip.
Since the formula is very pigmented, we suggest applying the colour to the bottom lip first, pressing your lips together and then filling in your Cupid's bow.

Product Name: Nude Spectrum Liquid Lip Matte with Hyaluronic Acid - Buttercream
Short Product Description: What it is: Lush, lustrous and lightweight, the Spectrum Liquid Lip is equal parts hydration boost and equal parts punchy when it comes to its colour and tone. The fuss-free, one-swipe application is luxuriously textured; the fade-free formula of the highly-pigmented shades are an all-occasion essential, as perfect for your daily makeup as it is for a wedding glam-up. The shades are meant to complement all the beautiful skin tones, meaning you can play it safe, or make your bold statement. After all, your makeup, your rules. Whats the science: The Spectrum Liquid Lip packs in hydration and plumping, healing chapped lips over time so you can apply it generously without fears of it feeling dry and cakey on your lips. Its hyaluronic acid (HA) content penetrates deep, giving the lips an instant, hydrated sheen and a natural volume throughout the day by retaining moisture. HA, a naturally occurring molecule and a multitasking ingredient has the ability to retain 1,000x its weight in water, keeping the tissues well-lubricated and moist, and the skin plump. It also improves the texture of the skin, fills in fine lines on the lips and increases its firmness while promoting collagen production.What else: The Spectrum Liquid Lip is loaded on the actives but sans any preservatives, mineral oil, and talc. The product is also PETA certified vegan and cruelty free.
